			"description": "Vietnamese has several particles that modify the tone of commands, making them softer, more urgent, or more insistent.",
			"particles": [
				{
					"particle": "đi",
					"function": "Soften, encourage",
					"effect": "Makes command feel like encouragement rather than order",
					"position": "After verb",
					"examples": [
						{
							"command": "Học đi!",
